## 5. Hook System ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

This is probably the most important thing.

Every transformer block should expose hooks.

Example

```
Before Attention

↓

After Attention

↓

After FFN

↓

After Block

↓

After Logits
```

Why?

Because RSVLM will eventually need access to

* hidden states

* attention maps

* logits

* entropy

without modifying GPT itself.

This will make the architecture incredibly clean.

